    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 180°C/ 160°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Deseed the<strong> peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min until roasted and golden – these are your <strong>roasted peppers</strong></p>",
