    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 700ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, then add the<strong> tomato paste</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and <strong>chilli relish </strong>– this is your<strong> sweet tomato stock</strong></p>",
