    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4 min until softened but not browned</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
