    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>arborio rice</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>ground turmeric</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further</p>",
