    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 1/3 of the <strong>sweet tomato stock</strong> and stir continuously until absorbed</p><p>Continue to add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sweet tomato stock</strong>, a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min, until all the stock has absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>risotto</strong></p>",
