    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, remove the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> from the oven</p><p>Stir <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>roasted pepper</strong> into the risotto (you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Remove the<strong> </strong>risotto from the heat and stir in<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped chives </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), then season with a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>sweet mixed pepper & chive risotto</strong></p>",
