    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top the<strong> sweet mixed pepper & chive risotto</strong> with the <strong>reserved roasted pepper</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated cheese </strong>and the <strong>pine nut & seed mix</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> reserved chopped chives</strong> and a<strong> </strong>drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
